  "libraryVersion": "2025.06",
  "lastValidated": "2026-06-27",
  "pluginNotes": "The SAP Figma library does NOT ship a distinct SearchField component. The plugin maps SearchField \u2192 Input instance and prepends a magnifier glyph in the placeholder when no leading icon is configured. SAP_KEYS: SearchField \u2192 'Input'. Status: AI specs MAY emit { component: 'SearchField', props: { placeholder: 'Filter X' } }. For visual consistency, prefer placing it after a ToolbarSpacer in OverflowToolbar.",
